'''薩克森花園'''（{{lang-pl|'''Ogród Saski'''}}）是位於[[波蘭|波蘭]]首都[[華沙|華沙]]的一座公園，面積15.5公頃<ref name="przewodnik">{{cite news |author =  |url = http://um.warszawa.pl/v_syrenka/zielona/?mi_id=43&dz_id=1 |title = Ogród Saski |work = ePrzewodnik |publisher =  |pages =  |page =  |date =  |accessdate = 2008-02-10 |language = pl |archive-date = 2008-04-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080408203450/http://um.warszawa.pl/v_syrenka/zielona/?mi_id=43&dz_id=1 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。薩克森花園是華沙歷史最久的公園，成立於17世紀，並在1727年對公眾開放<ref name="przewodnik" /><ref>[http://www.nathansvilla.com/warsaw_activities_attractions.html (english) nathansvilla.com] {{webarchive|url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080101023753/http://www.nathansvilla.com/warsaw_activities_attractions.html |date=2008-01-01 }} accessed 19 February 2008</ref>，是世界第一個對公眾開放的花園。

